Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.81,0:00:21.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Someone's wish is flying by again...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.06,0:00:26.28,Main,,0,0,0,,What... was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.28,0:00:30.24,Main,,0,0,0,,A wish upon a star that... I'm not aware of?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.78,0:00:37.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Releasing all the girls who\Nbecame LRIGs from their cards...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.66,0:00:44.25,Main,,0,0,0,,There's no way that Tama can make\Nthat wish come true when I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.25,0:00:46.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Yet, Ru...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.17,0:00:47.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Kominato Ruko is...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.84,0:00:49.42,Main,,0,0,0,,"White Room" "Large Window" "Mayu"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.42,0:00:49.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Hello...?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.97,0:00:51.55,Main,,0,0,0,,"Mayu"\NHello...?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.55,0:00:55.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you... Futase Fumio-{\i1}sensei{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.70,0:01:22.21,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Taken and granted,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.21,0:01:26.21,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ideals are repetitious games that slip through{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.21,0:01:28.92,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My daily life is so shot with holes{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.92,0:01:31.76,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that I can barely stand{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.76,0:01:33.09,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Empty theories without conclusions{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.09,0:01:37.26,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dance steps along invisible rules{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.26,0:01:42.27,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The final bell holding together{\i0}\N{\i1}the crumbling day rings{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.27,0:01:46.73,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In the scene I imagine{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.73,0:01:49.36,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}you're there{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.36,0:01:52.15,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}with a smile{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.15,0:01:57.66,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No forgiveness? No desires?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.66,0:02:01.08,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And still{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.75,0:02:05.92,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We cry "OPEN"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.92,0:02:10.30,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A future to get back and a world to destroy{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.30,0:02:12.76,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A wish to open. GOT IT?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.76,0:02:14.43,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now cross{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.43,0:02:17.09,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wish you don't cry{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.09,0:02:24.06,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The future of light and dark,{\i0}\N{\i1}let's believe in the "future"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.06,0:02:30.57,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}so that they overlap to gain color again{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.36,0:02:35.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you really...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.82,0:02:37.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.20,0:02:39.12,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm Futase Fumio.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.12,0:02:42.16,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought an adult was doing the writing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.16,0:02:44.96,Main,,0,0,0,,You're a... high school student?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.96,0:02:47.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Fujikou's uniform...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.21,0:02:50.13,Main,,0,0,0,,I'd never be able to get in there...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.80,0:02:54.47,Main,,0,0,0,,So, who will be battling us first?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.47,0:02:55.55,Main,,0,0,0,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.55,0:02:56.97,Main,,0,0,0,,...a Selector?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.97,0:03:00.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Let us now head to our stage of battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.97,0:03:04.81,Main,,0,0,0,,A high school girl author {\i1}and {\i0}a Selector?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.81,0:03:06.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Now things are heating up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.85,0:03:09.23,Main,,0,0,0,,It's like Chiyori's a burning chorizo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.23,0:03:13.15,Main,,0,0,0,,W-We didn't come here to battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.15,0:03:14.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.07,0:03:19.99,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't fathom any other reason why Selectors\Nwould get in contact aside from doing battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.99,0:03:23.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Battles shouldn't be held\Nbecause you're Selectors.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.33,0:03:26.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Now that is truly incomprehensible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.25,0:03:29.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't you girls have any\Nwish you want made true?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.25,0:03:31.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Wishes don't come true...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.79,0:03:34.30,Main,,0,0,0,,They come true, and yet... they don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.30,0:03:38.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Futase-{\i1}san{\i0}, I think you'll\Nunderstand if you learn the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.84,0:03:41.51,Main,,0,0,0,,The truth, hm...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.51,0:03:43.56,Main,,0,0,0,,You're an LRIG, so you should know!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.56,0:03:46.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Why yes, I do know...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.56,0:03:48.60,Main,,0,0,0,,But as luck would have it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.60,0:03:50.77,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm aware, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.77,0:03:53.07,Main,,0,0,0,,About this "truth" you speak of...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.07,0:03:57.32,Main,,0,0,0,,About what lies beyond Selector battles...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.32,0:03:58.66,Main,,0,0,0,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.66,0:04:01.82,Main,,0,0,0,,"The ruler of White Garden...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.82,0:04:05.91,Main,,0,0,0,,The almighty being that holds dominion\Nover all the WIXOSS battles...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.91,0:04:12.42,Main,,0,0,0,,The girl's lips speak\Nthe laws of the Selectors..."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.42,0:04:13.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.38,0:04:17.09,Main,,0,0,0,,The author... How much\Ndo you think she knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.01,0:04:22.80,Main,,0,0,0,,You really are a drag...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.80,0:04:24.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.72,0:04:27.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Wh-What did you just say...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.77,0:04:30.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Fumio said she knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.10,0:04:33.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Of what lies beyond the\Nbattles between Selectors.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.77,0:04:40.86,Main,,0,0,0,,A Selector who loses three times has\Ntheir wish reversed, with a cruel end in wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.86,0:04:45.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Assuming one continues to win\Nbattles to become an Eternal Girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.87,0:04:49.91,Main,,0,0,0,,...the one who fulfills the wish is\Nthe LRIG released from the card.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.91,0:04:55.25,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm also aware that the Selector\Nis then turned into an LRIG.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.25,0:04:57.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Then why are you still battling?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.80,0:05:01.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Nothing good can come from it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.05,0:05:03.18,Main,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.18,0:05:08.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Despite being Selectors,\Nyou girls deny Selector battles?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.48,0:05:10.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Quite an interesting take.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.35,0:05:13.94,Main,,0,0,0,,The Selectors who have come to\Nsee me after reading my novel...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.94,0:05:18.57,Main,,0,0,0,,...have all willingly accepted battle with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.57,0:05:21.78,Main,,0,0,0,,That's because of how you\Nwrote about it in your novel!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.78,0:05:23.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Futase-{\i1}san{\i0}, please tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.95,0:05:30.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't you... know more than\Nwhat's written in the novel?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.79,0:05:35.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Knowing that must be your wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.13,0:05:36.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.13,0:05:39.55,Main,,0,0,0,,If so, let us be like Selectors.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.55,0:05:44.51,Main,,0,0,0,,If you can defeat me in battle,\NI'll tell you everything that I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.51,0:05:45.85,Main,,0,0,0,,In battle...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.85,0:05:50.35,Main,,0,0,0,,There's no such thing as getting\Nsomething without doing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.35,0:05:54.06,Main,,0,0,0,,As an aside, Fumio hasn't lost once yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.06,0:05:56.15,Main,,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.15,0:05:57.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Me too...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.61,0:06:00.82,Main,,0,0,0,,The risks at hand lack excitement, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.82,0:06:04.28,Main,,0,0,0,,...in turn, I don't see\Nanything holding you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.32,0:06:07.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.83,0:06:11.33,Main,,0,0,0,,If Ruko-{\i1}san {\i0}doesn't wanna do it,\NChiyori wants to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.33,0:06:11.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.91,0:06:14.00,Main,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, wait a sec...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.00,0:06:16.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Aw, geez... this girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.33,0:06:19.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Does she even understand\Nshe's lost twice already?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.34,0:06:20.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Nah, not a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.42,0:06:24.30,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't care who faces me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.30,0:06:26.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.14,0:06:29.81,Main,,0,0,0,,It looks like it's decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.81,0:06:32.52,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll face that small lady there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.52,0:06:34.02,Main,,0,0,0,,--Yahoo!\N--I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.02,0:06:34.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.85,0:06:35.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.85,0:06:37.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.36,0:06:40.94,Main,,0,0,0,,We can't have you battle with\Nyour two losses, Chiyori-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.94,0:06:43.78,Main,,0,0,0,,--S-She nabbed my chance!\N--Hey! Read between the lines!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.95,0:06:46.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Please, Iona-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.91,0:06:48.16,Main,,0,0,0,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.37,0:06:52.50,Main,,0,0,0,,That LRIG...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.50,0:06:53.87,Main,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.87,0:06:55.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, let's begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.42,0:06:56.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Open!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.96,0:07:04.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's do this in grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.72,0:07:07.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Why does this have to happen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.68,0:07:09.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.14,0:07:12.51,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm... trying to do battle again...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.51,0:07:14.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Even after Tama said not to...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.77,0:07:19.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's open the show for an\Nenjoyable stage performance!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.52,0:07:24.40,Main,,0,0,0,,I go first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.40,0:07:26.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Grow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.32,0:07:28.24,Main,,0,0,0,,I summon Triumphal Arch and Clay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.24,0:07:29.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Grow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.62,0:07:33.58,Main,,0,0,0,,I Banish Triumphal Arch with Fallen Bind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.08,0:07:40.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Iona-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.00,0:07:41.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.80,0:07:42.75,Main,,0,0,0,,It's your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.75,0:07:44.30,Main,,0,0,0,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.30,0:07:47.05,Main,,0,0,0,,I Banish Puri with Slash Miracle!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.05,0:07:50.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Very well. I bring Surrelis to\Nmy hand with Puri’s ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.40,0:08:01.65,Main,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.65,0:08:06.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Without Tama, she's not\Nshowing her true potential...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.44,0:08:07.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.86,0:08:09.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Could that black LRIG be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.53,0:08:12.99,Main,,0,0,0,,So, you sense something from her, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.99,0:08:14.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Something different from us...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.79,0:08:18.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Something... special.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.33,0:08:22.00,Main,,0,0,0,,But, it looks like her affinity\Nwith her Selector is terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.00,0:08:24.13,Main,,0,0,0,,They aren't exhibiting their actual powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.13,0:08:26.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Well then, let's make them serious...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.77,0:08:44.23,Main,,0,0,0,,She's strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.23,0:08:47.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Her strategies are precise and effective...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.82,0:08:50.32,Main,,0,0,0,,...and she's a step ahead of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.32,0:08:53.41,Main,,0,0,0,,How much longer are you\Ngoing to worry indecisively?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.41,0:08:56.49,Main,,0,0,0,,I-I'm not being indecisive!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.49,0:08:59.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Before, you were hungry for battles
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.91,0:09:03.04,Main,,0,0,0,,and held strength to overcome\Nexpectations and experiences...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.04,0:09:04.84,Main,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.84,0:09:10.51,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't imagine you being\Nable to help anyone now...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.51,0:09:15.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Neither Yuzuki or any of the\Nother girls who became LRIGs...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.05,0:09:17.60,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll save them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.60,0:09:20.43,Main,,0,0,0,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.43,0:09:26.44,Main,,0,0,0,,I know the horrible things Hitoe went\Nthrough after her wish was reversed...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.44,0:09:33.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki did her best to have her wish\Ncome true, only to become an LRIG...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.07,0:09:34.70,Main,,0,0,0,,It's all horrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.70,0:09:37.53,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't want anyone to\Nexperience the same feelings!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.53,0:09:38.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Grow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.46,0:09:43.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Easier said than done.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.21,0:09:47.80,Main,,0,0,0,,I lost to you...! You, spewing out\Nthose despicable words!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.80,0:09:52.55,Main,,0,0,0,,To a fool, who was doing\Nher best to help others...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.55,0:09:56.55,Main,,0,0,0,,To such foolish purity...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.55,0:09:57.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Iona-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.76,0:10:04.44,Main,,0,0,0,,If you want to save everyone, don't let needless\Nthings sway you, and show your true self!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.44,0:10:08.77,Main,,0,0,0,,You're not the same as how you\Nwere when Tama was with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.77,0:10:12.40,Main,,0,0,0,,At this rate... you won't\Neven be able to save Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.45,0:10:15.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.62,0:10:25.21,Main,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.21,0:10:28.13,Main,,0,0,0,,I need to battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.13,0:10:30.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama... Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.96,0:10:33.01,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.01,0:10:35.09,Main,,0,0,0,,...save them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.09,0:10:37.43,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to dampen things, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.43,0:10:43.18,Main,,0,0,0,,...reality isn't like a story where you can\Nturn the tables to get out of a predicament.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.94,0:10:51.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.69,0:10:54.20,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't lose...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.40,0:10:57.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Iona-{\i1}san{\i0}, Grow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.24,0:10:58.16,Main,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.16,0:10:59.37,Main,,0,0,0,,What the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.37,0:11:01.16,Main,,0,0,0,,She's already Level 4!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.16,0:11:03.46,Main,,0,0,0,,There's no level higher than...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.04,0:11:07.83,Main,,0,0,0,,What's... that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.05,0:11:21.14,Main,,0,0,0,,What's with that form...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.14,0:11:24.43,Main,,0,0,0,,This is... Ruko's power...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.43,0:11:28.23,Main,,0,0,0,,The power that Tama felt from Ruko...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.23,0:11:30.15,Main,,0,0,0,,It... It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.15,0:11:33.53,Main,,0,0,0,,There's nothing in the scripts\Nof anything above Level 4...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.53,0:11:35.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Of a Level 5...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.49,0:11:39.16,Main,,0,0,0,,L-Lookie! We got a Level 5!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.16,0:11:42.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Could this be the forbidden power\Nthat awakens in a time of crisis?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.53,0:11:46.21,Main,,0,0,0,,What an exciting, and cliché turn of events!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.21,0:11:48.38,Main,,0,0,0,,It looks like Ruko... is having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.38,0:11:49.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.38,0:11:51.79,Main,,0,0,0,,But, that's the good Ruko, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.79,0:11:53.05,Main,,0,0,0,,I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.63,0:11:59.68,Main,,0,0,0,,It would be nice... to get an encore now...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.68,0:12:01.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Time to close the curtains.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.94,0:12:16.07,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry... Fumio...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.07,0:12:18.45,Main,,0,0,0,,No, that's fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.61,0:12:21.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Iona-{\i1}san{\i0}, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.91,0:12:25.45,Main,,0,0,0,,With your words, Iona-{\i1}san{\i0}, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.45,0:12:27.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.41,0:12:29.42,Main,,0,0,0,,...did I say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.38,0:12:38.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Level 5 was quite a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.01,0:12:39.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Your LRIG...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.17,0:12:41.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.09,0:12:45.72,Main,,0,0,0,,How much does Iona-{\i1}kun {\i0}know\Nabout the girl named "Mayu"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.72,0:12:47.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Mayu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.27,0:12:51.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Just so you know, I didn't tell her about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.10,0:12:56.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Fumio knew all about it,\Nfrom before she met me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.57,0:12:58.95,Main,,0,0,0,,What?! How...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.95,0:13:01.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Before being Futase Fumio...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.45,0:13:04.12,Main,,0,0,0,,...I was an LRIG.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.21,0:13:11.67,Main,,0,0,0,,An LRIG...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.67,0:13:17.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Th-Then... after returning as a human,\Nyou've become a Selector again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.05,0:13:19.30,Main,,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.30,0:13:22.22,Main,,0,0,0,,All in the name of a wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.39,0:13:26.22,Main,,0,0,0,,To fulfill...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.22,0:13:28.48,Main,,0,0,0,,...her wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.48,0:13:33.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Futase Fumio... is not my real name.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.98,0:13:37.15,Main,,0,0,0,,The name "Fumio" was...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.15,0:13:41.61,Main,,0,0,0,,...the name of a girl who was a Selector.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.61,0:13:43.57,Main,,0,0,0,,You can move?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.57,0:13:45.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Can't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.66,0:13:47.95,Main,,0,0,0,,So, you can talk, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.95,0:13:49.79,Main,,0,0,0,,You can hear me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.79,0:13:50.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.83,0:13:52.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.41,0:13:54.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.33,0:13:58.13,Main,,0,0,0,,You're not acting very surprised\Nfor hearing a card talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.30,0:14:03.93,Main,,0,0,0,,I've read a number of similar\Nstories like this already.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.01,0:14:07.81,Main,,0,0,0,,I guess introductions are in place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.81,0:14:09.52,Main,,0,0,0,,My name is Fumio.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.52,0:14:10.68,Main,,0,0,0,,What's yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.68,0:14:13.23,Main,,0,0,0,,I... forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.23,0:14:14.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Just name me whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.65,0:14:16.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.77,0:14:19.73,Main,,0,0,0,,...your name from today is "Futase."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.73,0:14:25.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes... Futase is the name\Nshe gave to me as an LRIG.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.28,0:14:29.74,Main,,0,0,0,,"The End of the World's Wings"\N"Side Story" "Volume Two"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.74,0:14:31.16,Main,,0,0,0,,"Fundamentals to Writing a Novel"\N"You're an Author Before you even Noticed"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.04,0:14:40.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Clicking and clacking every day...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.38,0:14:42.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Is that supposed to be fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.76,0:14:48.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Right now... no, it's not fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.26,0:14:50.97,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm a bit irritated because\NI have writer's block.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.97,0:14:53.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Then quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.31,0:14:55.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Sometimes, it's really fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.98,0:14:58.73,Main,,0,0,0,,There are moments I can\Nsense my accomplishments.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.90,0:15:02.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't you have anything like that, Futase?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.69,0:15:04.70,Main,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.70,0:15:09.58,Main,,0,0,0,,...don't care about dreams and wishes anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.58,0:15:12.58,Main,,0,0,0,,You make it sound like you had one before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.25,0:15:17.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Never mind. I won't ask anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.50,0:15:20.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Talk to me about it when\Nyou feel like it someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.92,0:15:27.38,Main,,0,0,0,,If you have a wish, you should just\Nlook for Selectors and do battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.38,0:15:29.43,Main,,0,0,0,,I suppose...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.43,0:15:34.43,Main,,0,0,0,,No matter my suggestions,\Nshe never partook in battles...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.23,0:15:39.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.44,0:15:41.86,Main,,0,0,0,,What do you mean you're not going to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.86,0:15:46.90,Main,,0,0,0,,There's no meaning to my dream if\NI don't attain it with my own hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.90,0:15:49.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Go and check on the others...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.16,0:15:51.58,Main,,0,0,0,,You don't have to tell me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.83,0:15:55.66,Main,,0,0,0,,She was lying...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.66,0:16:02.67,Main,,0,0,0,,An LRIG only appears to girls who\Nhave a wish they truly want to attain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.76,0:16:07.30,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.65,0:16:22.82,Main,,0,0,0,,No way...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.82,0:16:24.15,Main,,0,0,0,,C'mon, you're joking, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.15,0:16:26.07,Main,,0,0,0,,No, I'm super serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.07,0:16:27.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Whoops! We gotta go to another classroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.99,0:16:29.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Shoot! Let's hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.29,0:16:41.75,Main,,0,0,0,,That's a new card? That's so neat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.75,0:16:43.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.25,0:16:45.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Say, you want to battle me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.25,0:16:46.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Sure, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.42,0:16:48.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.88,0:16:54.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Didn't you buy the cards to play with someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.93,0:16:59.94,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm not well-suited for school life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.94,0:17:04.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Isn't it hell, not being able\Nto speak the whole day?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.86,0:17:07.44,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm used to it already.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.44,0:17:10.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Is it fun living like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.41,0:17:15.20,Main,,0,0,0,,A little, ever since I met you, Futase.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.20,0:17:16.99,Main,,0,0,0,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.99,0:17:20.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Say, look at that smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.08,0:17:25.46,Main,,0,0,0,,People smile when they're happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.47,0:17:33.97,Main,,0,0,0,,I became an LRIG and lost everything, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.97,0:17:38.68,Main,,0,0,0,,...as time passed...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.72,0:17:41.14,Main,,0,0,0,,"Author"\N"Futase Fumio"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.86,0:17:56.24,Main,,0,0,0,,...I began to wish in earnest,\Nfor her dream to come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.24,0:17:57.49,Main,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.83,0:18:02.50,Main,,0,0,0,,You've got some nerve,\Ndoing an overnighter again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.50,0:18:03.79,Main,,0,0,0,,I... I was working!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.79,0:18:06.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Liar... I bet you were with another woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.21,0:18:09.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Says the one fooling around\Nwith some other guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.09,0:18:16.26,Main,,0,0,0,,The reality that surrounded her...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.26,0:18:19.47,Main,,0,0,0,,...slowly gnawed away at her...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.47,0:18:22.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Even her last speck of hope...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.18,0:18:25.44,Main,,0,0,0,,...became shrouded by rain clouds...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.90,0:18:28.69,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.69,0:18:34.66,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm not interested in a Selector\Nwho's not interested in battling.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.66,0:18:37.03,Main,,0,0,0,,What if I say that I'll battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.03,0:18:38.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Fumio?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.20,0:18:39.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Oho!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.41,0:18:41.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Now you're talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.33,0:18:42.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, Fumio!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.83,0:18:46.46,Main,,0,0,0,,You need to get your wish\Nwith your own hands, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.46,0:18:47.79,Main,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.79,0:18:50.17,Main,,0,0,0,,That's right, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.17,0:18:51.96,Main,,0,0,0,,...I'm at my limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.96,0:18:57.01,Main,,0,0,0,,If my dream doesn't come true,\Nmy life would all be for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.01,0:19:02.14,Main,,0,0,0,,It's miserable just living\Nin futility like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.73,0:19:07.73,Main,,0,0,0,,So Futase, please lend me your hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.82,0:19:10.78,Main,,0,0,0,,I understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.78,0:19:15.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Then... I'll make your wish come true, Fumio.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.15,0:19:18.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Futase...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.28,0:19:22.33,Main,,0,0,0,,That's why... I'm your LRIG!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.45,0:19:26.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Now then, let's begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.00,0:19:27.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Open!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.04,0:19:31.38,Main,,0,0,0,,She was exceptional as a Selector.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.38,0:19:35.01,Main,,0,0,0,,She never lost a single time for her wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.01,0:19:38.01,Main,,0,0,0,,...and kept on winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.89,0:19:41.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.93,0:19:44.02,Main,,0,0,0,,I accept...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.02,0:19:46.81,Main,,0,0,0,,...the laws of the Selector.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.81,0:19:48.36,Main,,0,0,0,,And now...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.36,0:19:51.36,Main,,0,0,0,,...a new Eternal Girl will be born!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.11,0:19:57.86,Main,,0,0,0,,So now, my wish is going to come true...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.86,0:20:00.62,Main,,0,0,0,,...I'll make it come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.70,0:20:04.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Futase?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.41,0:20:07.87,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll make sure your wish comes true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.87,0:20:10.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.17,0:20:12.96,Main,,0,0,0,,What... are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.93,0:20:22.14,Main,,0,0,0,,The girl who dreamed of becoming a novelist...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.14,0:20:24.39,Main,,0,0,0,,...became an Eternal Girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.65,0:20:37.74,Main,,0,0,0,,The LRIG tasked with the girl's wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.74,0:20:40.07,Main,,0,0,0,,...went down the river of stars...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.07,0:20:45.29,Main,,0,0,0,,...and soon found the room\Nwhere the girl of fate slept.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.29,0:20:47.41,Main,,0,0,0,,The Girl of White...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.41,0:20:51.75,Main,,0,0,0,,...had a very beautiful, good heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.75,0:20:53.59,Main,,0,0,0,,On the other hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.59,0:20:58.76,Main,,0,0,0,,...the Girl of Black had\Na very unsightly, evil heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.38,0:21:08.35,Main,,0,0,0,,The Girl of Black envied and hated the\Never happy and smiling Girl of White...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.35,0:21:13.02,Main,,0,0,0,,...and thought of erasing her very existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.27,0:21:17.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Girl... of Black?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.82,0:21:23.62,Main,,0,0,0,,I sense something from her\Nthat's different from other LRIGs.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.12,0:21:26.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Iona-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.62,0:21:27.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Aren't you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.83,0:21:30.58,Main,,0,0,0,,...the Girl of Black?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.50,0:21:35.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Girl of Black...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.47,0:21:43.72,Main,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.72,0:21:45.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't, Iona...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.10,0:21:50.06,Main,,0,0,0,,The Girl of Black...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.06,0:21:53.98,Main,,0,0,0,,...can't become the Girl of White.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.98,0:21:56.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Longing of such...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.36,0:21:58.48,Main,,0,0,0,,...will dirty you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.48,0:22:00.15,Main,,0,0,0,,"This Impatience Is an Awakening"\N...will dirty you...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.15,0:22:02.53,Main,,0,0,0,,"This Impatience Is an Awakening"\N...to a shade of gray.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.87,0:23:35.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Girl of Black...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.25,0:23:38.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Girl of Dark...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.13,0:23:40.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Girl of Black...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.46,0:23:43.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Girl of Dark...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.13,0:23:44.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Truth is...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.63,0:23:46.93,Main,,0,0,0,,"That Existence is Dark Black"\NThat Existence is Dark Black.
